title: Evelyn Bermudez
text: I’m a fourth year, Economics and Environmental Studies double major. In addition to serving as the Undergraduate Economics Association’s Events Chair, I am a second-year Fellow in the Bren-Environmental Studies Fellowship. I also work in Dr. Samantha Stevenson’s Climate DataLab as an undergraduate researcher.
